:HELP NAME='DFIELD/KEYVAL'.Value
:XH3.Value
:P.A numeric value can be entered here.
:EHELP.
.* -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
:HELP NAME='DFIELD/VALFLD'.Text
:XH3.Text
